      "@id": "./",
      "@type": "Dataset",
      "name": "SciQuery: an expert-validated NL-to-SQL benchmark over scientific datasets",
      "description": "Expert-validated natural-language to PostgreSQL benchmark over 30 Dryad scientific datasets, with a paper-disjoint train/test split. Contains 673 gold items (520 train / 153 test) drawn from a 707-item candidate pool, with gold SQL, recorded answers, per-database schema metadata, and source provenance. Raw Dryad data are not redistributed; reconstruct databases from the original records listed in metadata/dryad_manifest.jsonl.",
